Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,You punk! How could you kill another one\Nof my darling chimeras?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:08.72,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:10.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Did he say 'darling'?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:13.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:16.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Get those two punks right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:17.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,But sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:19.50,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:22.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll have to get rid of\Nthese two on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:24.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:29.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,You ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:32.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Hey, I think we can use that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:33.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,And that over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:37.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:40.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Get your filthy hands off that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:43.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Let's take off, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:45.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Sir, are you starting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:48.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:54.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:00:58.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:05.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,As if...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:07.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:09.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Old man's got a good arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:14.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Hey Ed, where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:17.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Over there looks nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:19.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,There? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:24.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:28.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:30.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't that...
